== Useful Maven commands

Here's a list of some useful maven commands.

=== Release a new version
To prepare a new release

[source,bash]
----
 mvn clean install -Pdeploy,jetty,uat
----

NOTE: Please be patient - the first build might take even an hour

=== Tidy your poms
Another useful maven plugin is the Tidy plugin.

[source,xml]
----
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<settings>
	<servers>
		<server>
		</server>
	</servers>
</settings>
----


